### Render Booker Atom (JavaScript/TypeScript)

Source: https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/blob/main/docs/platform/atoms/booker.mdx

This snippet shows how to render the default Booker atom component. It requires the `eventSlug` and `username` props. The `onCreateBookingSuccess` callback can be used to handle successful booking events.

