### Install Cal.com Atoms Package

Source: https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/blob/main/docs/platform/quickstart.mdx

Instructions for installing the Cal.com atoms package using different package managers like npm, yarn, and pnpm. These atoms are UI components used for handling scheduling.

```bash
npm install @calcom/atoms
```

```bash
yarn add @calcom/atoms
```

```bash
pnpm add @calcom/atoms
```

