### Render Cal.com Booker Embed Atom

Source: https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/blob/main/docs/platform/atoms/booker-embed.mdx

This snippet demonstrates how to render the basic BookerEmbed atom, which allows users to book appointments directly on your website. It requires 'eventSlug' and 'username' as essential props. The 'onCreateBookingSuccess' callback can be used to handle successful booking events.

```javascript
