### Render Booker Atom with Week View (JavaScript/TypeScript)

Source: https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/blob/main/docs/platform/atoms/booker.mdx

This snippet demonstrates how to render the Booker atom with a 'WEEK_VIEW'. This view, along with 'COLUMN_VIEW', supports an Overlay Calendar feature for multi-calendar integration. The `view` prop is used to specify the layout.

```javascript
