### Setup Stripe in Event Types Atom - JavaScript

Source: https://github.com/calcom/cal.com/blob/main/docs/platform/atoms/payment-form.mdx

This snippet demonstrates how to set up the event types atom to accept payments. It requires the '@calcom/atoms' package. The component takes an event ID and renders the EventTypeSettings, which allows configuration of payment details like price and currency.

```javascript
import { EventTypeSettings } from "@calcom/atoms";

export default function EventType(id: number) {
      return (
          <>
            <EventTypeSettings id={id} allowDelete={true} />
          </>
      );
}
